l other aspects of a school wide technology approach can be addressed.  </p>\n\n<p>We go beyond &#8220;stuff&#8221; and address &#8220;staff&#8221;. We help students become better learners today and better earners tomorrow.</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,43],"assets/images/resized/0021/1849/211849v2-max-150x150.jpg"],[[250,72],"assets/images/resized/0021/1849/211849v2-max-250x250.jpg"],[[450,129],"assets/images/resized/0021/1849/211849v2-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":null},"products":[],"relationships":[{"is_past":false,"title":"Co-CEO and Co-founder","person":{"first_name":"Ernie","last_name":"Delgado","permalink":"ernie-delgado","image":null}}],"competitions":[],"providerships":[],"total_money_raised":"$0","funding_rounds":[],"investments":[],"acquisition":null,"acquisitions":[],"offices":[{"description":"Corporate Address","address1":"4195 Chino Hills Parkway","address2":"Suite 512","zip_code":"91709","city":"Chino Hills","state_code":"CA","country_code":"USA","latitude":null,"longitude":null}],"milestones":[],"ipo":null,"video_embeds":[{"embed_code":"<iframe width=\"430\" height=\"242\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/mmZnyXkD-uQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>","description":"<p>Who is BEYOND Technology Education? Watch and learn about SWIM Grid. </p>"}],"screenshots":[{"available_sizes":[[[150,48],"assets/images/resized/0020/0044/200044v2-max-150x150.jpg"],[[250,80],"assets/images/resized/0020/0044/200044v2-max-250x250.jpg"],[[450,145],"assets/images/resized/0020/0044/200044v2-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":null},{"available_sizes":[[[150,48],"assets/images/resized/0020/0045/200045v2-max-150x150.jpg"],[[250,80],"assets/images/resized/0020/0045/200045v2-max-250x250.jpg"],[[450,144],"assets/images/resized/0020/0045/200045v2-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":null},{"available_sizes":[[[150,47],"assets/images/resized/0020/0046/200046v2-max-150x150.jpg"],[[250,79],"assets/images/resized/0020/0046/200046v2-max-250x250.jpg"],[[450,143],"a